# Production-mode defaults for Docker / self-host / CI builds.
#
# The official openshock.app deployment's config (production URLs + SigNoz log/trace
# shipping) moved to `.env.cloudflare`, which is loaded ONLY by the Cloudflare Pages
# build (`pnpm build:cloudflare`, i.e. `vite build --mode cloudflare`). Keeping those
# values out of here means self-hosters no longer inherit openshock.app endpoints or
# SigNoz telemetry in their Docker images.
#
# Base defaults live in `.env`; self-hosters override per-deployment via docker-compose
# `environment:` (see docker-compose.yml). Add shared, non-official production overrides
# here if any are ever needed.
